						<summary>

						<p>Three fragments in Harijana-vāḍa.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>The purport of the three fragments is not clear. Only the below words can be made out from them. Fragment-1-Vasishṭa, Rāmadēva. -2-Paṁḍitā, Nāyaka. -3-Krōda, Vi(dya).</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 12th century A.D.</p>						

